<item>
            <title>[LU-882] Quota code causes run away ll_ost_io thread</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-882</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This is the NASA Ames installation.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;An ll_ost_io thread starts consuming 100% CPU on an OSS and eventually the OSS&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;becomes unresponsive (can&apos;t ssh or log in via serial console).&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;We had to disable quota to avoid the problems. See Bugzilla 23858.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Oracle pushed a fix to its prime b1_8. We would like Whamcloud to pick up the fix.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment>1.8.2 servers run sles10sp2 and 1.8.5 servers run centos 5.5.</environment>
